title: Get to Know TRICARE: Series 3, Episode 1 - Turning 65 Soon? Start Your TFL Checklist
description: Getting TRICARE For Life coverage starts with having Medicare Part A and Part B. Tune in to find out how you can sign up for Medicare and when your TFL coverage starts. Guest: Lennya Bonivento, Health Systems Analyst, Benefit Education and Research Team, Defense Health Agency
